response.overview: Jun-seok and Jong-jin, who are photographers, are close friends. The day of filming an underwear commercial is a vital energy for them, and Jun-seok often spends a strange time working with Seon-joo as an underwear model, but Jun-seok asks Jong-jin to find a model with big breasts. Jong-jin introduces Joo-hee, who was filmed the other day. Jun-seok likes C-cup Joo-hee, and Jun-seok gives Seon-joo the contact information of Jong-jin, who is looking for a leg model...
response.title: Good Giving Sisters
